            "SummaryExplanation": {
                "val": "FY19:  $36.779 million increase due to $25.000 million increase for restoration and modernization repairs to MCL, $3.000 million increase for the ARC Hypersonics Project, and $10.000 million increase for restoration and modernization repairs to National Full-Scale Aerodynamics Complex (NFAC) due to infrastructure failures, offset by a $1.221 million decrease to inflation adjustment for ongoing Service Life Extension Projects (SLEP)."
